dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Refer to this map as: 1:50,000, sheet ... edition, India." Sheets separately titled and numbered, e.g. Bhojpur, Patna and Sāran districts, Bihār, No. 72C/14. "Published under the direction of ... Surveyor General of India." Includes notes, index map to adjoining sheets, and administrative index.
